query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(pi it1) NoMergeJoin(it1 n pi ci) NoMergeJoin(ci it1 n pi t) NoHashJoin(ci it1 n pi t mi) NoHashJoin(ci it1 mi n pi t it2) */ select min(t.title),
min(pi.info)
from person_info AS pi
inner join info_type AS it1
on pi.info_type_id = it1.id AND pi.info ilike '%199%' AND it1.info ilike 'birth date'
inner join name AS n
on n.id = pi.person_id
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.person_id = n.id
inner join title AS t
on t.id = ci.movie_id
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info ilike '%sci%'
inner join info_type AS it2
on mi.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.id = 3;
